snippet.title: HYPERSTACKS VR Gameplay Trailer!
snippet.description:
#Hyperstacks #Indiegames2021 #VirtualReality 
Add the game to your Steam Wishlist! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1046760/Hyperstacks/
Early access available on App Lab https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/5022888091116866/
Join our Discord https://discord.gg/squirrelbytes

Hyperstacks is a combat-puzzle-platformer sandbox for VR, it includes a level editor to create your own content in-game
